---
const stepsData = [
  {
    id: 0,
    title: "Antes de empezar",
    isPrerequisite: true,
    content: `
      <div class="mb-6 p-5 bg-gradient-to-r from-indigo-500 to-purple-600 rounded-xl text-white">
        <div class="flex items-start gap-3">
          <div class="flex-shrink-0 w-10 h-10 rounded-lg bg-white/20 flex items-center justify-center">
            <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-white" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M9 12l2 2 4-4m6 2a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z" />
            </svg>
          </div>
          <div>
            <h3 class="font-bold text-lg mb-1">Lo que necesitas antes de comenzar</h3>
            <p class="text-white/90 text-sm">Asegúrate de tener todo esto listo para evitar problemas durante la instalación.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="grid gap-4 md:grid-cols-2">
        <div class="p-4 bg-slate-100 dark:bg-slate-800 rounded-xl">
          <div class="flex items-center gap-2 mb-3">
            <div class="w-8 h-8 rounded-lg bg-emerald-100 dark:bg-emerald-900/50 flex items-center justify-center">
              <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-emerald-600 dark:text-emerald-400" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M3 8l7.89 5.26a2 2 0 002.22 0L21 8M5 19h14a2 2 0 002-2V7a2 2 0 00-2-2H5a2 2 0 00-2 2v10a2 2 0 002 2z" />
              </svg>
            </div>
            <h4 class="font-semibold text-slate-800 dark:text-slate-200">Cuenta de MiniMax.io</h4>
          </div>
          <ul class="text-sm text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-400 space-y-1">
            <li>• API Key lista (empieza con <code class="px-1 py-0.5 bg-slate-200 dark:bg-slate-700 rounded text-xs">eyJ...</code>)</li>
            <li>• Creditos disponibles</li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <div class="p-4 bg-slate-100 dark:bg-slate-800 rounded-xl">
          <div class="flex items-center gap-2 mb-3">
            <div class="w-8 h-8 rounded-lg bg-purple-100 dark:bg-purple-900/50 flex items-center justify-center">
              <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-purple-600 dark:text-purple-400" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M7 20l4-16m2 16l4-16M6 9h14M4 15h14" />
              </svg>
            </div>
            <h4 class="font-semibold text-slate-800 dark:text-slate-200">Workspace de Slack</h4>
          </div>
          <ul class="text-sm text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-400 space-y-1">
            <li>• Acceso de admin para crear apps</li>
            <li>• Capacidad de instalar apps</li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <div class="p-4 bg-slate-100 dark:bg-slate-800 rounded-xl">
          <div class="flex items-center gap-2 mb-3">
            <div class="w-8 h-8 rounded-lg bg-blue-100 dark:bg-blue-900/50 flex items-center justify-center">
              <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-blue-600 dark:text-blue-400" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M21 12a9 9 0 01-9 9m9-9a9 9 0 00-9-9m9 9H3m9 9a9 9 0 01-9-9m9 9c1.657 0 3-4.03 3-9s-1.343-9-3-9m0 18c-1.657 0-3-4.03-3-9s1.343-9 3-9m-9 9a9 9 0 019-9" />
              </svg>
            </div>
            <h4 class="font-semibold text-slate-800 dark:text-slate-200">Cuenta de Google</h4>
          </div>
          <ul class="text-sm text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-400 space-y-1">
            <li>• Acceso a Google Cloud Console</li>
            <li>• Spreadsheets compartidos (para Sheets)</li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <div class="p-4 bg-slate-100 dark:bg-slate-800 rounded-xl">
          <div class="flex items-center gap-2 mb-3">
            <div class="w-8 h-8 rounded-lg bg-amber-100 dark:bg-amber-900/50 flex items-center justify-center">
              <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-amber-600 dark:text-amber-400" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M9.75 17L9 20l-1 1h8l-1-1-.75-3M3 13h18M5 17h14a2 2 0 002-2V5a2 2 0 00-2-2H5a2 2 0 00-2 2v10a2 2 0 002 2z" />
              </svg>
            </div>
            <h4 class="font-semibold text-slate-800 dark:text-slate-200">Windows 10 o 11</h4>
          </div>
          <ul class="text-sm text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-400 space-y-1">
            <li>• Permisos de administrador</li>
            <li>• Conexión a internet</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="mt-6 p-4 bg-amber-50 dark:bg-amber-900/30 border border-amber-200 dark:border-amber-800 rounded-xl">
        <div class="flex items-start gap-3">
          <div class="flex-shrink-0 w-8 h-8 rounded-lg bg-amber-100 dark:bg-amber-900/50 flex items-center justify-center">
            <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-amber-600 dark:text-amber-400" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M12 8v4l3 3m6-3a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z" />
            </svg>
          </div>
          <div>
            <h4 class="font-semibold text-amber-900 dark:text-amber-300 text-sm mb-1">Tiempo estimado</h4>
            <p class="text-amber-800 dark:text-amber-300 text-sm">La instalación completa toma aproximadamente <strong>30-45 minutos</strong>. Asegúrate de tener suficiente tiempo antes de comenzar.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="mt-6 p-4 bg-emerald-50 dark:bg-emerald-900/30 border border-emerald-200 dark:border-emerald-800 rounded-xl">
        <div class="flex items-start gap-3">
          <div class="flex-shrink-0 w-8 h-8 rounded-lg bg-emerald-100 dark:bg-emerald-900/50 flex items-center justify-center">
            <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-emerald-600 dark:text-emerald-400" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M13 10V3L4 14h7v7l9-11h-7z" />
            </svg>
          </div>
          <div>
            <h4 class="font-semibold text-emerald-900 dark:text-emerald-300 text-sm mb-1">¿Dónde encontrar tus tokens?</h4>
            <div class="text-emerald-800 dark:text-emerald-300 text-sm space-y-2 mt-2">
              <div>
                <strong>MiniMax API Key:</strong> Panel de MiniMax.io → API Keys
              </div>
              <div>
                <strong>Slack Tokens:</strong> api.slack.com/apps → Tu App → OAuth & Permissions / Socket Mode
              </div>
              <div>
                <strong>Google:</strong> console.cloud.google.com → APIs & Services → Credentials
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    `
  },
  {
    id: 0,
    title: "Glosario de términos",
    isGlossary: true,
    content: `
      <div class="space-y-4">
        <div class="p-4 bg-slate-100 dark:bg-slate-800 rounded-xl">
          <h4 class="font-semibold text-slate-800 dark:text-slate-200 text-sm mb-2 flex items-center gap-2">
            <span class="w-6 h-6 rounded-full bg-indigo-100 dark:bg-indigo-900/50 text-indigo-600 dark:text-indigo-300 text-xs flex items-center justify-center">1</span>
            PowerShell / Terminal
          </h4>
          <p class="text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-400 text-sm">Programa donde escribes comandos de texto. En Windows 11 ya viene instalado Windows Terminal.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="p-4 bg-slate-100 dark:bg-slate-800 rounded-xl">
          <h4 class="font-semibold text-slate-800 dark:text-slate-200 text-sm mb-2 flex items-center gap-2">
            <span class="w-6 h-6 rounded-full bg-indigo-100 dark:bg-indigo-900/50 text-indigo-600 dark:text-indigo-300 text-xs flex items-center justify-center">2</span>
            Node.js
          </h4>
          <p class="text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-400 text-sm">Programa que permite ejecutar código JavaScript. Necesario para OpenCode.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="p-4 bg-slate-100 dark:bg-slate-800 rounded-xl">
          <h4 class="font-semibold text-slate-800 dark:text-slate-200 text-sm mb-2 flex items-center gap-2">
            <span class="w-6 h-6 rounded-full bg-indigo-100 dark:bg-indigo-900/50 text-indigo-600 dark:text-indigo-300 text-xs flex items-center justify-center">3</span>
            pnpm
          </h4>
          <p class="text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-400 text-sm">Herramienta para instalar programas. Similar a npm pero más rápida.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="p-4 bg-slate-100 dark:bg-slate-800 rounded-xl">
          <h4 class="font-semibold text-slate-800 dark:text-slate-200 text-sm mb-2 flex items-center gap-2">
            <span class="w-6 h-6 rounded-full bg-indigo-100 dark:bg-indigo-900/50 text-indigo-600 dark:text-indigo-300 text-xs flex items-center justify-center">4</span>
            Variable de entorno
          </h4>
          <p class="text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-400 text-sm">Guarda información persistente en Windows. Se usa para guardar tokens y contraseñas de forma segura.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="p-4 bg-slate-100 dark:bg-slate-800 rounded-xl">
          <h4 class="font-semibold text-slate-800 dark:text-slate-200 text-sm mb-2 flex items-center gap-2">
            <span class="w-6 h-6 rounded-full bg-indigo-100 dark:bg-indigo-900/50 text-indigo-600 dark:text-indigo-300 text-xs flex items-center justify-center">5</span>
            Token / API Key
          </h4>
          <p class="text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-400 text-sm">Contraseña especial que identifica tu cuenta. Comienza con xoxb-, xapp-, eyJ... según el servicio.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="p-4 bg-slate-100 dark:bg-slate-800 rounded-xl">
          <h4 class="font-semibold text-slate-800 dark:text-slate-200 text-sm mb-2 flex items-center gap-2">
            <span class="w-6 h-6 rounded-full bg-indigo-100 dark:bg-indigo-900/50 text-indigo-600 dark:text-indigo-300 text-xs flex items-center justify-center">6</span>
            MCP (Model Context Protocol)
          </h4>
          <p class="text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-400 text-sm">Sistema que permite a OpenCode conectarse con herramientas externas como Slack y Google.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="p-4 bg-slate-100 dark:bg-slate-800 rounded-xl">
          <h4 class="font-semibold text-slate-800 dark:text-slate-200 text-sm mb-2 flex items-center gap-2">
            <span class="w-6 h-6 rounded-full bg-indigo-100 dark:bg-indigo-900/50 text-indigo-600 dark:text-indigo-300 text-xs flex items-center justify-center">7</span>
            GCP (Google Cloud Platform)
          </h4>
          <p class="text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-400 text-sm">Plataforma de Google donde se configuran las APIs de Calendar y Sheets.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="p-4 bg-slate-100 dark:bg-slate-800 rounded-xl">
          <h4 class="font-semibold text-slate-800 dark:text-slate-200 text-sm mb-2 flex items-center gap-2">
            <span class="w-6 h-6 rounded-full bg-indigo-100 dark:bg-indigo-900/50 text-indigo-600 dark:text-indigo-300 text-xs flex items-center justify-center">8</span>
            Service Account
          </h4>
          <p class="text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-400 text-sm">Cuenta especial de Google para que programas accedan a Sheets automáticamente.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="p-4 bg-slate-100 dark:bg-slate-800 rounded-xl">
          <h4 class="font-semibold text-slate-800 dark:text-slate-200 text-sm mb-2 flex items-center gap-2">
            <span class="w-6 h-6 rounded-full bg-indigo-100 dark:bg-indigo-900/50 text-indigo-600 dark:text-indigo-300 text-xs flex items-center justify-center">9</span>
            Socket Mode
          </h4>
          <p class="text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-400 text-sm">Método de conexión de Slack que usa WebSockets en lugar de HTTP. Permite recibir eventos en tiempo real.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="p-4 bg-slate-100 dark:bg-slate-800 rounded-xl">
          <h4 class="font-semibold text-slate-800 dark:text-slate-200 text-sm mb-2 flex items-center gap-2">
            <span class="w-6 h-6 rounded-full bg-indigo-100 dark:bg-indigo-900/50 text-indigo-600 dark:text-indigo-300 text-xs flex items-center justify-center">10</span>
            OAuth / Consent Screen
          </h4>
          <p class="text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-400 text-sm">Pantalla donde autorizas que una aplicación acceda a tu cuenta de Google.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    `
  },
  {
    id: 1,
    title: "Instalar Windows Terminal y PowerShell",
    content: `
      <div class="mb-6 p-4 bg-blue-50 dark:bg-blue-900/30 border border-blue-200 dark:border-blue-800 rounded-xl">
        <div class="flex items-start gap-3">
          <div class="flex-shrink-0 w-8 h-8 rounded-lg bg-blue-100 dark:bg-blue-900/50 flex items-center justify-center">
            <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-blue-600 dark:text-blue-400" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M13 16h-1v-4h-1m1-4h.01M21 12a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z" />
            </svg>
          </div>
          <div>
            <h3 class="font-semibold text-blue-900 dark:text-blue-300 text-sm mb-1">¿Qué es Windows Terminal?</h3>
            <p class="text-blue-800 dark:text-blue-300 text-sm leading-relaxed">Windows Terminal es una aplicación moderna de terminal para Windows que permite usar PowerShell y otras terminales de forma más cómoda y visual.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <h3 class="text-base font-semibold text-slate-800 dark:text-slate-200 mb-3 flex items-center gap-2">
        <span class="flex items-center justify-center w-5 h-5 rounded-full bg-indigo-100 dark:bg-indigo-900/50 text-indigo-600 dark:text-indigo-300 text-xs font-bold">1.1</span>
        Instalar desde Microsoft Store
      </h3>
      <ol class="space-y-2 mb-6 text-sm text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-400">
        <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
          <span class="flex-shrink-0 w-5 h-5 rounded-full bg-indigo-100 dark:bg-indigo-900/50 text-indigo-600 dark:text-indigo-300 text-xs font-medium flex items-center justify-center mt-0.5">1</span>
          <span>Abre la <strong class="text-slate-800 dark:text-slate-200">Microsoft Store</strong> en tu computadora</span>
        </li>
        <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
          <span class="flex-shrink-0 w-5 h-5 rounded-full bg-indigo-100 dark:bg-indigo-900/50 text-indigo-600 dark:text-indigo-300 text-xs font-medium flex items-center justify-center mt-0.5">2</span>
          <span>En el buscador, escribe: <code class="px-1.5 py-0.5 bg-slate-100 dark:bg-slate-700 rounded text-slate-700 dark:text-slate-300 font-mono text-xs">Windows Terminal</code></span>
        </li>
        <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
          <span class="flex-shrink-0 w-5 h-5 rounded-full bg-indigo-100 dark:bg-indigo-900/50 text-indigo-600 dark:text-indigo-300 text-xs font-medium flex items-center justify-center mt-0.5">3</span>
          <span>Busca la app de <strong class="text-slate-800 dark:text-slate-200">Microsoft Corporation</strong></span>
        </li>
        <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
          <span class="flex-shrink-0 w-5 h-5 rounded-full bg-indigo-100 dark:bg-indigo-900/50 text-indigo-600 dark:text-indigo-300 text-xs font-medium flex items-center justify-center mt-0.5">4</span>
          <span>Click en <strong class="text-slate-800 dark:text-slate-200">"Instalar"</strong></span>
        </li>
      </ol>

      <h3 class="text-base font-semibold text-slate-800 dark:text-slate-200 mb-3 flex items-center gap-2">
        <span class="flex items-center justify-center w-5 h-5 rounded-full bg-indigo-100 dark:bg-indigo-900/50 text-indigo-600 dark:text-indigo-300 text-xs font-bold">1.2</span>
        Instalar PowerShell
      </h3>
      <ol class="space-y-2 mb-6 text-sm text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-400">
        <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
          <span class="flex-shrink-0 w-5 h-5 rounded-full bg-slate-100 dark:bg-slate-700 text-slate-500 dark:text-slate-400 text-xs font-medium flex items-center justify-center mt-0.5">1</span>
          <span>En Microsoft Store, busca: <code class="px-1.5 py-0.5 bg-slate-100 dark:bg-slate-700 rounded text-slate-700 dark:text-slate-300 font-mono text-xs">PowerShell</code></span>
        </li>
        <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
          <span class="flex-shrink-0 w-5 h-5 rounded-full bg-slate-100 dark:bg-slate-700 text-slate-500 dark:text-slate-400 text-xs font-medium flex items-center justify-center mt-0.5">2</span>
          <span>Instala <strong class="text-slate-800 dark:text-slate-200">"PowerShell"</strong> (la versión más reciente)</span>
        </li>
      </ol>

      <h3 class="text-base font-semibold text-slate-800 dark:text-slate-200 mb-3 flex items-center gap-2">
        <span class="flex items-center justify-center w-5 h-5 rounded-full bg-indigo-100 dark:bg-indigo-900/50 text-indigo-600 dark:text-indigo-300 text-xs font-bold">1.3</span>
        Abrir Windows Terminal
      </h3>
      <ol class="space-y-2 mb-6 text-sm text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-400">
        <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
          <span class="flex-shrink-0 w-5 h-5 rounded-full bg-slate-100 dark:bg-slate-700 text-slate-500 dark:text-slate-400 text-xs font-medium flex items-center justify-center mt-0.5">1</span>
          <span>Presiona la tecla <strong class="text-slate-800 dark:text-slate-200">Windows</strong> en tu teclado</span>
        </li>
        <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
          <span class="flex-shrink-0 w-5 h-5 rounded-full bg-slate-100 dark:bg-slate-700 text-slate-500 dark:text-slate-400 text-xs font-medium flex items-center justify-center mt-0.5">2</span>
          <span>Escribe <code class="px-1.5 py-0.5 bg-slate-100 dark:bg-slate-700 rounded text-slate-700 dark:text-slate-300 font-mono text-xs">Terminal</code> o <code class="px-1.5 py-0.5 bg-slate-100 dark:bg-slate-700 rounded text-slate-700 dark:text-slate-300 font-mono text-xs">Windows Terminal</code></span>
        </li>
        <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
          <span class="flex-shrink-0 w-5 h-5 rounded-full bg-slate-100 dark:bg-slate-700 text-slate-500 dark:text-slate-400 text-xs font-medium flex items-center justify-center mt-0.5">3</span>
          <span>Click en el icono para abrirlo</span>
        </li>
      </ol>

      <div class="p-4 bg-slate-900 dark:bg-slate-800 rounded-xl">
        <p class="text-sm text-slate-400 dark:text-slate-500 mb-2">Verás algo como:</p>
        <code class="text-emerald-400 font-mono text-sm">PS C:\Users\TuNombre&gt;</code>
      </div>
    `
  },
  {
    id: 2,
    title: "Instalar Node.js",
    content: `
      <div class="mb-6 p-4 bg-blue-50 dark:bg-blue-900/30 border border-blue-200 dark:border-blue-800 rounded-xl">
        <div class="flex items-start gap-3">
          <div class="flex-shrink-0 w-8 h-8 rounded-lg bg-blue-100 dark:bg-blue-900/50 flex items-center justify-center">
            <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-blue-600 dark:text-blue-400" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M13 16h-1v-4h-1m1-4h.01M21 12a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z" />
            </svg>
          </div>
          <div>
            <h3 class="font-semibold text-blue-900 dark:text-blue-300 text-sm mb-1">¿Qué es Node.js?</h3>
            <p class="text-blue-800 dark:text-blue-300 text-sm leading-relaxed">Node.js es un programa necesario para ejecutar OpenCode y otras herramientas de desarrollo.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <h3 class="text-base font-semibold text-slate-800 dark:text-slate-200 mb-3">Descargar Node.js</h3>
      <ol class="space-y-2 mb-6 text-sm text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-400">
        <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
          <span class="flex-shrink-0 w-5 h-5 rounded-full bg-indigo-100 dark:bg-indigo-900/50 text-indigo-600 dark:text-indigo-300 text-xs font-medium flex items-center justify-center mt-0.5">1</span>
          <span>Abre tu navegador (Edge, Chrome, etc.)</span>
        </li>
        <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
          <span class="flex-shrink-0 w-5 h-5 rounded-full bg-indigo-100 dark:bg-indigo-900/50 text-indigo-600 dark:text-indigo-300 text-xs font-medium flex items-center justify-center mt-0.5">2</span>
          <span>Ve a: <a href="https://nodejs.org/" target="_blank" class="text-indigo-600 dark:text-indigo-400 hover:underline font-medium">nodejs.org</a></span>
        </li>
        <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
          <span class="flex-shrink-0 w-5 h-5 rounded-full bg-indigo-100 dark:bg-indigo-900/50 text-indigo-600 dark:text-indigo-300 text-xs font-medium flex items-center justify-center mt-0.5">3</span>
          <span>Click en el botón <strong class="text-slate-800 dark:text-slate-200">"LTS"</strong> (Recommended for most users)</span>
        </li>
        <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
          <span class="flex-shrink-0 w-5 h-5 rounded-full bg-indigo-100 dark:bg-indigo-900/50 text-indigo-600 dark:text-indigo-300 text-xs font-medium flex items-center justify-center mt-0.5">4</span>
          <span>Sigue las instrucciones del instalador y espera a que termine</span>
        </li>
      </ol>

      <h3 class="text-base font-semibold text-slate-800 dark:text-slate-200 mb-3">Abrir Windows Terminal con PowerShell</h3>
